            <Header/>
            <Routes>

                  <Route path='/Recursos' element={<Recursos/>}/>
                  <Route path='/Covid' element={<covid-19/>}/>
                  <Route path='/Capac' element={<Capac/>}/>

      </Router>
     )


export default App
